---
title: Flat-Top Burger with Cornmeal Crusted Pickles and Fries
description: Presenting the cornmeal-crusted pickle burger! A classic flat-top burger topped with cornmeal oven-fried pickles and dressed to perfection. There's no better way to kick off summer!
